volume.name: The Return of Lum * Urusei Yatsura Part Three

description:
translation: The Mystery of the Dead Blondes

Are Johnnie and son Kees indeed the murderers of all the blond girls in Zonnedael? Or has a mistake been made? And why has daughter Kees suddely red hair? Ma Flodder meets a new man on the Internet. But their first meeting is almost fatal. Luckily grandpa makes sure all ends well.

The Mystery of the Dead Blondes is the first hilarious part of a new comic series about the most famous and infamous family of the Netherlands!

Written by the same team behind the successful films and tv series, Dick Maas and Wijo Koek.
name: Het Mysterie van de Dode Blondjes
Michel Vaillant: Steve Warson gaat K.O.
